ANALYSIS
This bill directs hospitals, ambulatory surgical centers, and emergency medical care centers to
develop a screening and treatment plan for venous thromboembolism. The bill also directs the
department of health and human services to contract with a qualified entity to establish and
maintainastatewidevenousthromboembolismregistry.
